"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1930557-Alex-Yee-Team-GB-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympicsilver medallist Hayden Wilde has claimed he was punched in the face during the triathlon final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999755802553754, \"rank\": 1.5797265346295403e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The New Zealander looked certain to claim the gold medal when he went into the final lap with an impressive lead.\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, his triumph ended in extraordinary fashion, asGreat Britain's Alex Yee found an extra gearand overtook Wilde in the final stages of the race.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999755802553754, \"rank\": 1.5797265346295403e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Yee continues to revel in Olympic glory, Wilde took to social media to claim he was on the wrong end of some physical treatment from other triathletes.\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999755802553754, \"rank\": 1.5797265346295403e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He claimed he was struck in the face and had his feet grabbed and dragged down by other racers.\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old even showed off a bruise on his chin that he claimed was suffered in the race.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998781277, \"rank\": 1.2190417931968383e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999978643422832, \"rank\": 2.1356616719907216e-06, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When he uploaded the selfie, showcasing the mark on his chin, he said: \\\"Good punch in the face on the swim.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Probably one of the most aggressive swims in a long time, grabbing feet and pushed down.\\\"\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three hours later, he played down what had happened in another Instagram story.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.4092251312650084e-28, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"But do not worry, that's part of racing.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Would not have changed the results.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loved that battle, so good!\\\"\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee was 14 seconds away from Wilde when he began his final lap.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999755802553754, \"rank\": 1.5797265346295403e-05, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also 18th coming out of the water but managed to move himself to the front when he hopped on his bike.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His triumph followed the silver medal he won in the same event at the Tokyo Games in 2021, where he also won gold in the triathlon mixed relay.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After his victory in the French capital, he said: \\\"I still do not really know what to say to be honest.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1738, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7904767052855428, \"rank\": 0.23505426795793907, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a bit lost for words and so grateful to everyone who's been in my corner for the last three years.\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was for them.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At 5km I was going through a really bad patch.\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With 2.5km to go I thought, I am going to give myself one last chance at this and not give up, and here we are.\\\"\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Before Yee's heroics, former 10,000m track star Beth Potter won Britain's first triathlon medal of the day when she earned a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Potter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She looked back on her last Olympics at Rio de Janeiro 2016, where she was still a track athlete.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While reminiscing, she said: \\\"Eight years ago, I watched Vicky Holland on Copacabana, and I was on the track team,\\\" she said after her third place finish.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vicky Holland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vicky_Holland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have come a long way in eight years.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did it for me, but also for everyone that has helped me in the past eight years.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They believed in me from day one, so it's for them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5644153157080447e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3102, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5644153157080447e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"